## Dual Licensing Model

This project adopts a **Dual Licensing Model**. You may choose the applicable license based on your use case:

| Use Case | Applicable License | Cost |
|----------|-------------------|------|
| Personal use | AGPL v3.0 | Free |
| Non-profit organizations / Educational institutions | AGPL v3.0 | Free |
| Medical institutions / Medical research organizations | AGPL v3.0 | Free |
| Enterprise internal use ≤1000 installations (AGPL compliant) | AGPL v3.0 | Free |
| Enterprise internal use >1000 installations | Commercial License | Paid |
| Enterprise closed-source use / No intention to open-source modifications | Commercial License | Paid |
| Providing SaaS services based on this project | Commercial License | Paid |
| Embedding this project in commercial products for distribution | Commercial License | Paid |
| Modifying software Logo or name | Commercial License | Paid |
| Removing or modifying "Support the Author" feature | Commercial License | Paid |

